<h1 class="title">TheAmericanExperiment</h1>
<p>
The American experiment is an example of <a href="PerfectionNotRequired.html#ID-B10A6829-648A-4AC6-9E78-F75330BC1457">PerfectionNotRequired</a>. The country was far from perfect when formed (in fact it was deeply flawed). But it had a way to self improve, and with time the notion of a citizen improved and expanded to be more perfect.
</p>


